    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in good overall condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use, including light surface scratches, but no significant dents or rust. The interior is clean with moderate wear on the seats and trim. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained adequately for its age and mileage.",
